(2000001627,'Naga warlord! Oh dear...', 0, 0, 0, 5, NULL),
(2000001628,'Well, you aren\'t going to like what I have to tell you, young missy. This tablet is a naga communication. Their leader, Warlord Sriss\'tiz, has ordered his naga to take the rest of the island by force.', 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL),
(2000001629,'And it looks like he\'s got reinforcements comin\' from Nazjatar!', 0, 0, 0, 5, NULL),
(2000001630,'We\'ve got to do something about this!', 0, 0, 0, 5, NULL),
(2000001631,'Thank you, Adamant. I think I know just the person for the job.', 0, 0, 0, 2, NULL);
